com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation

Class JsonAutoDetect.Value

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonAutoDetect.Value
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JacksonAnnotationValue<JsonAutoDetect>, Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    JsonAutoDetect

    public static class JsonAutoDetect.Value
extends Object
implements JacksonAnnotationValue<JsonAutoDetect>, Serializable
    Helper class used to contain information from a single JsonIgnoreProperties annotation, as well as to provide possible overrides from non-annotation sources.
    Since:
    2.9
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
